notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the samba SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 8.8. It addresses 7 CVEs: CVE-2022-2127, CVE-2023-34966, CVE-2023-34967, CVE-2023-34968, CVE-2023-3961, and 2 more.
